data.description: Step inside this Gorgeous DR Horton home- (Rockdale Floorplan). Built in 2021, 4-bed, 2-bath home in the heart of Mansfield. Open concept with beautiful wood look tile throughout common areas. kitchen with quartz countertops, a large island, gas cooktop, and separate wall oven. Custom build shiplap wall with electric fireplace in living room The primary suite offers a spacious  bedroom, bathroom with shower and garden tub, plus a walk-in closet. Outside, a large covered patio for relaxing and entertaining complete with an oversized backyard,  19 x 19 turf area with in ground basketball goal. Garage has epoxy-coated floor as well as an insulated garage door.
